====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|anatomy|lang=en}} The region back of the [[knee]] [[joint]]; the [[popliteal]] space; the [[hock]].
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A [[thigh]] and [[buttock]] of an animal slaughtered for meat.
# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} Meat from the thigh of a [[hog]] cured for food.
#: ''a little piece of '''ham''' for the cat''
#* {{rfdate}}, Audra Lilly Griffeth, ''A King's Daughter'' (ISBN 146915532X):
#*: She put some '''ham''' in the beans and cut up some sweet potatoes to boil.
# The back of the thigh.
# {{context|internet|informal|lang=en}} [[electronic mail|Electronic mail]] that is wanted; mail that is not [[spam]] or [[junk mail]].

